{{note|This page is about an [[ACS]] function. For a similar [[ZScript]] function see '''[[A_SetMugshotState]]'''.}}
void '''SetMugShotState'''(str ''state'')
== Usage == Used to set the state of the [[mugshot]] as defined in [[SBARINFO]]. The state you set will only be interrupted by damage or if the player picks up a weapon, provided the mugshot supports it.
== Examples == The following example will make the player believe that they are invulnerable or make spectators think he/she is cheating. script 1 (void) { [[SetMugShotState]]("God"); }
